node.text:
After 488 days away from the fans, it was an honor to be able to perform live for you all again last Friday night in H-town. The energy in the building was electrifying, and I have you all to thank for that. It was amazing to see everything come full circle that night. From the time when Dominik was just a child, playing around with Edge backstage, to sharing the ring with both of them for Dominik’s live debut, is a blessing I can only thank 🙏🏼God for. It was truly a night I will never forget and I want to thank each and everyone of you who was in attendance that night, as well as all the fans at home. It’s all of your Love & support that keeps us going! 
L💙ve y’all back  #Mysterios🇲🇽 
Los quier🤍un chingo #VivaLaRaza🇲🇽

Booyaka

Link in bio to order now!

node.text:
I had so many pictures 2 choose from but picked this one cuz it shows your true natural beauty!! 

Happy 20th Birthday my baby girl, my lil princess 👑 

Wasn’t able 2 spend the day with you but was happy & blessed 2 have giving you your hug last night……..also want 2 let you know how proud I am of your dedication & determination on everything you set your heart & soul to !! 

Really hope you enjoyed your day with your friends & family, I L💙ve you so much mija & just know that you will always be my lil princess!!
#Happy2️⃣0️⃣th 🥳🎂 #Daddy’sLilGirl
